const styles = {
    inputDiv : {
      display: 'flex',
      width: '87%',
      height: '48px',
      boxSizing: 'border-box',
      padding: '14px',
      border:0,
      backgroundColor: 'white',
      margin:'0 6.5%',
      borderBottom: '1px solid lightgray',
      justifyContent: "space-between"
    },

  checkBox:{
    width: '20px',
    height: '20px',
    borderRadius: '50%',
    display: 'flex',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    marginRight: '12px',
    border: '1px solid lightgray'
  },
  checkBoxChecked:{
    width: '20px',
    height: '20px',
    borderRadius: '50%',
    display: 'flex',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #55DDFF 0%, #C058F3 100%)',
    marginRight: '12px',
    border: '1px solid lightgray'
  },
}
  

  export default styles;
